{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-html-elements-with-selectors-using-jquery","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Manipulacija HTML elementima korišćenjem selektora pomoću jQuery-ja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada imamo funkcionalnost od <code>document ready</code>.</p>\n<p>Sada napišite naš prvi jQuery deklarativni izraz. Sve jQuery funkcije počinju sa <code>$</code>, često se nazivaju znak dolar, ili bling.</p>\n<p>jQuery često bira element sa HTML za <dfn>selektori</dfn>, zatim radi nešto s tim elementom.</p>\n<p>Na primer, neka svi tvoji elementi za <code>button</code> preskoče/skaču. Dodaj ovaj kod unutar svoje funkcije za 'document ready':</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">$(\"button\").addClass(\"animated bounce\");\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamtite da smo već uključili biblioteku jQuery i biblioteku Animate.css u pozadini kako biste mogli da ih koristite u editoru. Stoga koristite jQuery da dodelite klasu <code>bounce</code> iz Animate.css za vaše elemente <code>button</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9bedc08826","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18319,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-html-elements-with-selectors-using-jquery"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.2.0/animate.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite funkciju <code>addClass()</code> iz jQuery-ja da dodelite klase <code>animated</code> i <code>bounce</code> vašim elementima <code>button</code>.</p>","testString":"assert($('button').hasClass('animated') && $('button').hasClass('bounce'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite jQuery samo za dodavanje ovih klasa elementu.</p>","testString":"assert(!code.match(/class.*animated/g));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš jQuery kod treba da bude unutar funkcije <code>$(document).ready();</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  code.replace(/\\s/g, '').match(/\\$\\(document\\)\\.ready\\(function\\(\\)\\{\\$/g)\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#jquery","dashedName":"target-html-elements-with-selectors-using-jquery","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoop